I like that he said to stick around for more of whatever this is.
It's TRUE because at this point anywhere you go all you hear about is the coronavirus info, so it's like we are beyond the point of it being news. And for a late night show where they also focus on entertainment to help the celebrities continue their business, Nowadays we can't really even do that because it kinda takes the back seat.
This is all very interesting to be witnessing, specially as a 28 year old who had her 1st ER visit this week Wednesday. I'm young but I'm trying to stay calm and be a beacon of hope for myself and for others around me.
If you made it to this point, thanks for reading. Stay safe, happy and kind.
